FILE STRUCTURE:
- cards.py (79 lines):
  * Suit enum (HEARTS, DIAMONDS, CLUBS, SPADES)
  * Rank enum (2-ACE with values)
  * Card class with get_value() method
  * Deck class with shuffle/deal/remaining

- hand_logic.py (62 lines):
  * calculate_hand_value() - Smart Ace handling (soft/hard)
  * compare_hands() - Determine win/loss/bust/push

- game.py (203 lines):
  * BlackjackGame class - Main state machine
  * Methods: place_bet, deal_initial_hands, player_hit, player_stand
  * Natural blackjack detection
  * Out-of-money recovery
  * Balance tracking
  
- window.py (453 lines):
  * DialogButton class for UI buttons
  * OutOfMoneyDialog for balance reset
  * GameModeScreen for mode selection
  * BlackjackWindow main game window
  * Event handling, rendering, game loop
  * ESC key returns to mode select

